Couffin - A simple PHP shopping basket.                                    
Ver 1.1

Installation
------------
- Make sure you have PHP installed
- Copy all the files into your working directory
- Make sure that your PHP process has write access to the "invoice-sequence" file.

Getting started
---------------
- Edit your settings in "config/settings.php"
- Edit your product catalog in "config/products.php". Place your product images in the "images" folder.
- Edit "config/paymentProcessor.php". This is the form that should get securely posted to your
payment processor.
- Configure your payment processor to hand over the flow back to "success.php" or "failure.php" page.
- Customize the php templates to your liking.
- You should not alter the files in the class directory.